
- Top page
  http://localhost:8888
  (http://localhost:8888/index.html)
  

- DTO / Database entities
 User
   -key
   -id (userid)
   -name (username)
   -token
   -timestamp
   
 Event
   -key
   -id (eventid)
   -subject
   -place
   -eventDate
   -registeredDate
   -expiredDate
   -number
   -comment
   -owner (ownerRef --> User)
   -participants (participantsRef --> Participant) 
   -timestamp

 Participant
   -key
   -event (eventRef --> Event)
   -user (userRef --> User)
   -comment
   

